data.description: Enjoy country living on 3 acres in Monroe County.  Unique opportunity offering 2 homes.  Main house with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths.  Great kitchen with granite countertops, farmhouse sink & eating bar.  Spacious great room and office on main level.  Loft area perfect for second living/flex space.  Large master suite with private bath, garden tub & separate shower.  Second home/guest house approx 1000 sqft, with 2 bedrooms, full bath & living area.  So much space for outdoor living, including rocking chair front porches & patio.  Cleaned pasture area for animals, garden spot or recreation.  Spring fed creek on property.
